<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Perfect Fit - shop for fitness goods</mj-title>
    <mj-font name="Iter" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter&display=swap" />
    <mj-style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        font-family: "Iter", sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: normal;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Iter", sans-serif;
        background: #fafafa;
        color: #515759;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-size: 16px;
        padding: 48px 60px 58px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      div,
      p {
        font-size: inherit;
        color: #515759 !important;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .goods-img img {
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .button-product {
        display: inline-block;
        border: 1px solid #1890ff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 1px 15px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 22px;
        font-weight: normal;
        vertical-align: text-top;
        margin-left: 10px;
      }

      .title {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 22px;
        color: #0c1014;
        margin: 24px 0 16px;
      }

      .good {
        margin-bottom: 48px !important;
      }

      .footer {
        padding-top: 16px;
        border-top: 1px solid #d6d7d9;
      }

      .footer-copy {
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .link-style {
        font-size: inherit;
        color: #1890ff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .link-style:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        body {
          padding: 48px 20px 58px;
        }
        .title {
          font-size: 20px;
          line-height: 0.95;
        }
      }
      @media (max-width: 380px) {
        .title {
          font-size: 18px;
        }
      }
    </mj-style>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-all padding="0" />
      <mj-button inner-padding="1px 15px" background-color="transparent">
        <mj-text color="#515759" padding="24px 0 16px" />
    </mj-attributes>
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body width="640px">
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image align="center" width="114px" height="24px" src="img/logo.png" alt="Logotype" />
        <mj-text padding="32px 0" align="center">
          <p>Hi Sam! Here‚Äôs your weekly updates üëÄÔ∏è</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-wrapper css-class="goods">
      <mj-section css-class="good">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-image css-class="goods-img" src="img/img1.png" alt="img1" />
          </mj-image>
          <mj-text>
            <h2 class="title">Here Are the Best Sneakers of 2019<a class="button-product" href="#!">New</a></h2>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            <p>We‚Äôre still quite early into the year, but it‚Äôs never too soon to highlight our picks for the best sneakers of the year, so far.</p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section css-class="good">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-image css-class="goods-img" src="img/img2.png" alt="img2" />
          </mj-image>
          <mj-text>
            <h2 class="title">8 Drops You Don't Want to Miss This Week</h2>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            <p>Supreme Fall 2019 Collection Week 2, Palace Fall 2019 Collection Week 5, Travis Scott: Look Mum I Can Fly Customizable Merch and more.</p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section css-class="good">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-image css-class="goods-img" src="img/img3.png" alt="img3" />
          </mj-image>
          <mj-text>
            <h2 class="title">We opened a store in Warsaw</h2>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            <p>The store focuses on up-and-coming brands that are doing really innovative and exciting things that may ruffle a few feathers while setting the trends and inspiring today‚Äôs youth culture.</p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
    </mj-wrapper>
    <mj-section css-class="footer">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>
          <p>
            This email was sent to you as a registered member of prfctfit.com.
            To update your emails preferences <a class="link-style" href="#!">click here.</a>
            Use of the service and website is subject to our <a class="link-style" href="#!">Terms of Use and Privacy Statement.</a>
          </p>
          <p class="footer-copy">¬© 2019 PRFCT FIT. All rights reserved</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
